  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Function Returns"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- If there is a `return` statement in a function, the value of the expression following `return` will be sent back."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 24,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "60"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 24,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def calc_sum(x, y, z):\n",
    "    return x + y + z\n",
    "    print('This will be ignored')\n",
    "\n",
    "r = calc_sum(10, 20, 30)\n",
    "r"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 25,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "None\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def calc_sum(x, y, z):\n",
    "    r = x + y + z\n",
    "\n",
    "r = calc_sum(10, 20, 30)\n",
    "print(r)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- If there is no `return` statement or just the keyword `return` but nothing follows, the function sends back a special object `None`."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 26,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "None\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def calc_sum(x, y, z):\n",
    "    r = x + y + z\n",
    "    return\n",
    "\n",
    "r = calc_sum(10, 20, 30)\n",
    "print(r)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 27,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
